e similar to that in the electromagnetic\ncase. The strong analogy suggests a gauge invariant definition of helicity for\nnon-abelian gauge fields. We will provide further support for this view.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Nov 2018 02:10:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
