lerating systems identified by combining Hipparcos and\nGaia. Our analysis could be repeated for many of them to build a large sample\nof companions with dynamical masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Nov 2018 06:37:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Feb 2019 04:51:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-01"}
